{"tid":1718930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個燒街鋪邊個就係鬼","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T06:01:15.000Z","uid":24730,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b383a5124ebcde1da83b545f08821526d2ccffcb","tid":1718930,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"呢兩日喺屋企藍絲人嘅社交群組圈子，見到佢地好期待火燒店鋪會蔓延民居，佢哋覺得只要燒死幾個無辜市民，就可以扭轉整個輿情。<br />\n<br />\n跪求勇武裝修就算，無謂燒鋪。亦擔心有黑警/黑幫燒鋪嫁禍勇武，如見到有店鋪著火，請前線協助立即救火，切勿傷害無辜市民，而且樓上居民可能係手足"},{"pid":"9b6be1e6fbe35a2e7790517050001c39facdc1ee","tid":1718930,"uid":113922,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"1f1a059de45a501ccbc626910b8b2d39d7aa34b5","tid":1718930,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"樓主=鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871ff785e2a7dc090dd97940a9646cbe00d726aa","tid":1718930,"uid":146027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"鬼你老母 依家做任何野都有機會傷及無辜市民 咁佢哋又係鬼？"},{"pid":"5c9054d04e6bc534c0d2d737eef5a77d5168204b","tid":1718930,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"話我係鬼都要推，燒鋪係最無謂最無效益嘅事，黑警最期待就係你燒鋪燒死市民，唔會喺度勸你唔好燒"},{"pid":"afc3c638b71f2207e78bd0d2cb789470a09673ef","tid":1718930,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛 blocked"},{"pid":"1c4b1c6554c62e26355c5b8987c30b97a76a55d7","tid":1718930,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好畀國會緃火案喺民居發生，否則成個國際戰線都會崩潰</span></span>"},{"pid":"72f4fac84ca84843ee7a6ab9a5e106f41fccb92f","tid":1718930,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"7c4504140179aaefb5c095d537db147d32a2